[vc_row full_width="" parallax="" parallax_image="" launchkit_padding="" background_style="full" align=""][vc_column width="1/1"][launchkit_slider parallax="fixed-header" short="header-11 overlay"][launchkit_slider_content image="64"]

Frequently Asked Questions

[/launchkit_slider_content][/launchkit_slider][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="" parallax="" parallax_image="" launchkit_padding="" background_style="light-wrapper" align=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="" width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
Is Launchkit a WordPress theme?
Hell yes! It's a simple to use WordPress theme based on Visual Composer and really clean code. It's super easy to use and you'll love it![/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="32px"][vc_column_text]
Will there be a Launchkit for WordPress?
Yeah, it's right here! We've spent the past few months perfecting Launchkit for WordPress and I'm sure you're going to love what we've done with it!
[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="32px"][vc_column_text css_animation=""]
How many landing pages can I create?
You may create as many pages as you like per single project. This means that if you plan to use Launchkit for another project, you will need to purchase an additional standard license.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="32px"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="" width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
Do you provide support for Launchkit?
Yes - we provide support for Launchkit via our dedicated support forum which is detailed in the theme docs. This includes general item support but not additional customisation services.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="32px"][vc_column_text]
Are PSD files included in the download?
While the PSD files are not included in the download package from Envato (due to file-size), you can contact us via our support forum and we will happily provide them for you.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="32px"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="" width="1/1"][vc_column_text]

Still have questions? Let us know on Themeforest!

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]
